* sch_x=0 sch_y=0 sch_r=None
Xq1 n2 n1 0 0 npn13G2 Nx=10 dtemp=0 Ny=1 le=959.9999999999999n we=119.99999999999999n selft=1 sw_nqs=0
* sch_x=-50 sch_y=0 sch_r=None
Xr1 n4 n1 0 rsil dx=8 dy=2
